California flyers . ..

san Jose nonstop
• Ski Heavenly Easy Sunjet
Tours to Lake Tahoe
• New Daily nonstops between
San Francisco and Palm Springs

Palm Springs, Ontario, Sacramento, San Francisco,
Oakland, San Jose and Lake Tahoe.
